Package it.cnr.isti.labsedc.glimpse.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IncorrectRuleFormatException
    This exception will be thrown when the Monitoring Manager
    will receive an invalid rule.
    The rule is contained into the field RuleBody of the ComplexEventRuleDocument object
    UnknownConsumerIDException
    This exception will be thrown when the Monitoring Manager
    is unable to find the ID of the Consumer that send a evaluation request.
    UnknownEnablerIDException  
    UnknownRuleException
    This exception will be thrown when the Monitoring Manager
    is unable to complete the request of unloading a rule.
